Package org.apache.storm.security.auth

Class ReqContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.storm.security.auth.ReqContext
  • public class ReqContext
extends Object
    Request context. Context request context includes info about:
    1. remote address
    2. remote subject and primary principal
    3. request ID
